      "signature": "public void _ProcessModification()",
      "returnType": "void",
      "parameters": [],
      "summary": "Override this virtual method to implement a custom skeleton modifier. You should do things like get the [Skeleton3D]\u0027s current pose and apply the pose here. [method _process_modification] must not apply [member influence] to bone poses because the [Skeleton3D] automatically applies influence to all bone poses set by the modifier.",
